fm: vector<int> nextGreaterElements(vector<int> &nums) {         int n = nums.size();         stack<int> s;         vector<int> ret(n, -1);         for (int i = 0; i < n * 2; ++i) {             while (!s.empty() && nums[s.top()] < nums[i % n]) {                 ret[s.top()] = nums[i % n];                 s.pop();             }             if (i < n)                 s.push(i);         }         return ret;     }

fm: vector<string> findRelativeRanks(vector<int> &nums) {         int n = nums.size(), j = 0;         vector<Athlete> athletes(n, Athlete());         vector<string> ret(n, "");         vector<string> medal{"Gold Medal", "Silver Medal", "Bronze Medal"};         for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {             athletes[i].score = nums[i];             athletes[i].pos = i;         }         sort(athletes.begin(), athletes.end(), [](const Athlete &a1, const Athlete &a2) {             return a1.score >= a2.score;         });         for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i)             ret[athletes[i].pos] = j <= 2 ? medal[j++] : to_string(i + 1);         return ret;      }

fm: int fib(int N) {         if(N == 0)             return 0;         int i = 0, j = 1;         while (N > 1) {             int temp = i + j;             i = j;             j = temp;             --N;         }         return j;     }
